%% 3.2.17 View Transaction History — sequence
%% GET /api/Wallet/TransactionHistory/{walletId}?fromDate&toDate&method&status
%% Or TransactionLog/Search if using shared ledger API
%% BR71: Append-only ledger

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Guardian as Guardian
    participant App as Mobile App
    participant WC as WalletController
    participant WS as WalletService
    participant Repo as TransactionLog Wallet
    participant DB as SQL Server

    Guardian->>App: Open transaction log in Wallet
    App->>WC: GET /api/Wallet/TransactionHistory/{walletId} with filters
    WC->>WS: GetTransactionHistoryAsync
    WS->>Repo: Query logs
    Repo->>DB: SELECT
    WS-->>WC: paged history
    WC-->>App: 200 OK — green credits / red debits
